    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>orzo</strong> to the pan and cook for 1 min</p><p>Add the <strong>stock</strong> and <strong>soft cheese</strong> and cook, covered, stirring frequently, for 10-12 min, or until the orzo is cooked with a slight bite and the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p><p>Tip: Stirring the orzo will release the starch from the pasta, making it creamier!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
