        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped spinach, halved cherry tomatoes </strong>and <strong>grated cheese</strong> to the <strong>orzo</strong> with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>torn</strong> <strong>basil leaves</strong> (save the rest for later!) and cook until the spinach has wilted</p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>creamy chicken breast florentine</strong></p>",
